In [[music]], '''protoculture''' is a alternative rock fusion band from Los Angeles, California. formed in 1994 by guitarist Steve Abbagon, bass player John Burkes, and drummer Trevor Jayne. Protoculture continues to tour around the country preforming with such artists as Incubus, Fiona Apple, Perry Ferrell, Jill Scott, and Woven.[http://www.myspace.com/protoculture][http://www.http://wovenmusic.com/]  

